简并子空间为：<span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3618-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-113761" style="width: 6.804em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.655em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.204em 1000em 3.487em -0.52em); top: -3.095em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113762"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113763" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113764" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">p</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113765" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113766" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113767" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">{</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113768"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113769" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113770" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113771" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟩</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113772" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">,</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113773" style="padding-left: 0.188em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113774" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-