<li><h3 class="wmd-title">能量的一阶修正</h3>

<p>由于微扰:<span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><div class="MathJax_Display" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style="text-align: center;"><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3619-Frame" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-113778" style="width: 10.589em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.81em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.205em 1000em 5.986em -0.46em); top: -4.345em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113779"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113780" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">V<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.077em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113781" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113782" style="padding-left: 0.313em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113783" style="vertical-align: 1.962em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.45em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXSizeOneSym; top: -3.288em; left: 0em;">⎛<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXSizeOneSym; top: -0.864em; left: 0em;">⎝<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: STIXSizeOneSym; position: absolute; top: -2.48em; left: 0em;">⎜<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: STIXSizeOneSym; position: absolute; top: -1.672em; left: 0em;">⎜<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-113784"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113785"><span class="mtable" id="MathJax-Span-113786" style="padding-right: 0.167em; padding-left: 0.167em;"><span style="display: inline-block