   0 & {\lambda a} & {\lambda b}  \cr 
   {\lambda {a^*}} & 0 & 0  \cr 
   {\lambda {b^*}} & 0 & 0  \cr } } \right)</script>
可以微扰V 在简并子空间<span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3620-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-113835" style="width: 6.804em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.655em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.204em 1000em 3.487em -0.52em); top: -3.095em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113836"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113837" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113838" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">p</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113839" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113840" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113841" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">{</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113842"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113843" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113844" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113845" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟩</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113846" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">,</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113847" style="padding-left: 0.188em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113848" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113849" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113850" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟩</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113851" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">}</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.095em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.254em; vertical-align: -0.327em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-3620">span\{\left|2 \right\rangle,\left| 3\right\rangle\}</script>里已经块对角化了，则能量的一阶修正量是微扰矩阵块对角化后的相应对角元素，所以能量的一阶修正都是0：<span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><div class="MathJax_Display" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style="text-align: center;"><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3621-Frame" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-113852" style="width: 11.589em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.643em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.523em 1000em 3.026em -0.537em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113853"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-113854"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.144em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.728em 1000em 2.738em -0.537em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113855" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.023em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.605em 1000em 2.44em -0.457em); top: -2.642em; left: 0.712em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-113856"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113857"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113858" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.605em 1000em 2.44em -0.457em); top: -1.984em; left: 0.632em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-113859"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113860"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113861" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113862" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113863" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113864" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">,</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-113865" style="padding-left: 0.188em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.144em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.728em 1000em 2.738em -0.537em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113866" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.023em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.605em 1000em 2.44em -0.457em); top: -2.642em; left: 0.712em;"><span cla