(1.605em 1000em 2.45em -0.507em); top: -1.984em; left: 0.632em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-113881"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113882"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113883" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">3</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113884" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113885" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">0</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.518em; vertical-align: -0.417em;"></span></span></nobr></span></div><script type="math/tex; mode=display" id="MathJax-Element-3621">E_{1}^{1}=0,E_{2}^{1}=0,E_{3}^{1}=0</script>.</p></li>
<li><h3 class="wmd-title">能量的二阶修正</h3>

<p>在简并子空间 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3622-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-113886" style="width: 6.804em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.655em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.204em 1000em 3.487em -0.52em); top: -3.095em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113887"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113888" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113889" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">p</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113890" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113891" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113892" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">{</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113893"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113894" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113895" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113896" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟩</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113897" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">,</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113898" style="padding-left: 0.188em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113899" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inli