可以块对角化微扰矩阵 V，并且可以使得能量的二级修正不再简并，在非简并子空间 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3625-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-113971" style="width: 4.875em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.048em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.204em 1000em 3.487em -0.52em); top: -3.095em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113972"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113973" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113974" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">p</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113975" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113976" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113977" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">{</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-113978"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113979" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113980" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113981" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟩</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-113982" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">}</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.095em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-styl