<p>将能量本征值和波函数都按照 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3628-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-114034" style="width: 0.589em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.476em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.703em 1000em 2.754em -0.548em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114035"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-114036" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">λ</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0.976em; vertical-align: -0.091em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-3628">\lambda</script> 展开，得到下式:
