<p>按照 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3630-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-114133" style="width: 1.089em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.893em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.141em 1000em 2.397em -0.548em); top: -2.202em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114134"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-114135"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.908em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.703em 1000em 2.754em -0.548em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-114136" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">λ</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -2.667em; left: 0.476em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114137" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.222em; vertical-align: -0.091em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-3630">\lambda^1</script> 提项：</p>

