<p>左乘 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3632-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-114197" style="width: 1.446em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.19em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.204em 1000em 3.487em -0.459em); top: -3.095em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114198"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114199"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114200" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟨</span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114201" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114202" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.095em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.254em; vertical-align: -0.327em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-3632">\left\langle 2 \right|</script>    （<strong>这个是难点</strong>）:</p>

