<p>由于前面已经求得了能量的一阶修正，带入上式：</p>

<p><span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><div class="MathJax_Display" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style="text-align: center;"><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3634-Frame" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-114278" style="width: 21.375em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.798em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.347em 1000em 4.057em -0.459em); top: -3.452em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114279"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114280"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114281" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">⟨</span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114282" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114283" style="vertical-align: 0.713em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.251em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114284" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">0</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114285"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114286" style="vertical-align: 0.891em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -2.895em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span clas