<p>消去含 0 的项，并且注意到 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3635-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-114343" style="width: 3.732em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.095em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.523em 1000em 3.026em -0.537em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114344"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-114345"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.144em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.728em 1000em 2.738em -0.537em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-114346" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.023em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.605em 1000em 2.45em -0.519em); top: -2.642em; left: 0.712em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-114347"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114348"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114349" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">0</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.605em 1000em 2.44em -0.457em); top: -1.974em; left: 0.632em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-114350"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114351"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114352" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114353" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-114354" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic; padding-left: 0.313em;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.023em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.518em; vertical-align: -0.417em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-3635">E_{1}^{0} = E</script> 和 <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-3636-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-114355" style="width: 5.161em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.286em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.347em 1000em 4.057em -0.536em); top: -3.452em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114356"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-114357"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114358" style="vertical-align: 0.881em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.266em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -3.298em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; top: -2.915em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-114359"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.968em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.705em 1000em 2.738em -0.425em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-114360" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -2.6