<h3 class="wmd-title" id="mathjax">MathJax</h3>

<p>You can render <em>LaTeX</em> mathematical expressions using <strong>MathJax</strong>, as on [math.stackexchange.com][1]:</p>

<p>The <em>Gamma function</em> satisfying <span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2746-Frame" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-85227" style="width: 12.518em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.417em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.705em 1000em 2.915em -0.525em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-85228"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85229" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">Γ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85230" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85231" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85232" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85233" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85234" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85235" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85236" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.25em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-85237" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.25em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85238" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85239" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">!</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-85240" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 1.125em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85241" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">∀</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85242" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85243" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">∈</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-85244" style="padding-left: 0.313em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-85245"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85246" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">ℕ</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 1.166em; vertical-align: -0.284em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2746">\Gamma(n) = (n-1)!\quad\forall
n\in\mathbb N</script> is via through the Euler integral</p>

<p><span class="MathJax_Preview"></span><div class="MathJax_Display" role="textbox" aria-readonly="true" style="text-align: center;"><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2747-Frame" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-85247" style="width: 11.018em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.167em; height: 0px; font-size: 120%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.965em 1000em 3.668em -0.525em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-85248"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85249" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">Γ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85250" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85251" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">z</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85252" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85253" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.313em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-85254" style="padding-left: 0.313em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.127em 1000em 4.754em -0.48em); top: -3.69em; left: 0em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85255" style="font-family: STIXIntegralsD; vertical-align: -0.615em;">∫<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.45em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.69em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.779em 1000em 2.44em -0.486em); top: -3.373em; left: 1.197em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85256" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">∞</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.605em 1000em 2.45em -0.519em); top: -1.342em; left: 0.562em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-85257" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">0</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-85258" style="padding-left: 0.188em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.559em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.835em 1000em 2.749em -0.498em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85259" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">t<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.018em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -2.675em; left: 0.353em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-85260"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-85261"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85262" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">z</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85263" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-85264" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-85265"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.265em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.94em 1000em 2.749em -0.505em); top: -2.56em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85266" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">e</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -2.675em; left: 0.476em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-85267"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-85268"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85269" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85270" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">t<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.013em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.262em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85271" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.027em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-85272" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">t<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.018em;"></span></span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-85273" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.188em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-85274" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">.</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.56em;"></span></span></span><span style="border-left-width: 0em; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 2.957em; vertical-align: -1.187em;"></span></span></nobr></span></div><script type="math/tex; mode=display" id="MathJax-Element-2747">
\Gamma(z) = \int_0^\infty t^{z-1}e^{-t}dt\,.
</script></p>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong>NOTE:</strong> When exporting, make sure you include MathJax to render mathematical expression correctly. Your page/template should include something like: </p>
</blockquote>

<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted" style=""><code><span class="tag">&lt;script</span><span class="pln"> </span><span class="atn">type</span><span class="pun">=</span><span class="atv">"text/javascript"</span><span class="pln"> </span><span class="atn">src</span><span class="pun">=</span><span class="atv">"http://cdn.mathjax.org/mathjax/latest/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS_HTML"</span><span class="tag">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></code></pre>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong>NOTE:</strong> You can find more information:</p>
  
  <ul>
  <li>about <strong>Markdown</strong> syntax [here][2],</li>
  <li>about <strong>Markdown Extra</strong> extension [here][3],</li>
  <li>about <strong>Prettify</strong> syntax highlighting [here][4],</li>
  <li>about <strong>Highlight.js</strong> syntax highlighting [here][5].</li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

